      "title": "Research Scope",
      "body": "The research covers 21 jurisdictions as of Registry v59: the original 19 NAPCS states plus Hawaii and Wisconsin, added in May 2026. The 584-school NAPCS baseline is supplemented by a Discovery Schools program that identifies and documents organized charter schools outside the baseline universe — 23 approved discoveries to date, assigned PLT-issued NAPCS-ADD identifiers and given full research treatment.\n\nThe project is designed for biannual refresh — current cycle closes October 2026 — with the data architecture built to support rolling updates without rebuilding from scratch."
